    "announcerProfile": "arena-announcer",
    "gameStart": "The ancient coliseum ship drifts into orbit. Force fields shimmer as two warriors from across the galaxy take their positions. The stars themselves bear witness. Let the duel begin!",
    "roundStart": [
      "Thrusters fire and the arena platform rotates. A new round of combat ignites beneath the twin suns!",
      "The nebula pulses with light as the combatants circle each other. Another exchange begins!",
      "Starship engines roar overhead. The crowd of a thousand species cheers as the next round commences!",
      "Shields recharge and weapons hum with fresh power cells. The warriors engage once more!",
      "The galactic anthem fades. Silence grips the coliseum. Then the clash resumes!"
    ],
    "roundEndTie": [
      "The force fields equalize â€” neither warrior gains ground. The galaxy holds its breath!",
      "Blasters cool and blades retract. A stalemate across the stars!"
    ],
    "criticalHit": [
      "A devastating strike tears through shields! Sparks and starlight collide!",
      "Direct hit to the core! The crowd erupts across a dozen worlds!",
      "The force of that blow echoes through the void! Absolutely devastating!"
    ],
    "criticalMiss": [
      "A wild shot arcs into the void! The targeting systems fail spectacularly!",
      "The weapon misfires in a shower of sparks! A costly mistake!",
      "The strike goes wide, scorching the arena wall! The stars seem to mock that attempt!"
    ],
    "lowHpTension": [
      "Warning klaxons wail as both warriors trail smoke and sparks. The end draws near.",
      "Shield generators flicker on both sides. One final strike could decide the fate of empires.",
      "The coliseum falls silent. Both combatants battered and bleeding under alien skies. This is the moment."
    ]
